overview: Bull protects his not-so-small younger brother from the outside world, but who protects the outside world from Tickles. A team of YouTube paranormal activity seekers comes to a haunted attraction in the backwoods to find more than they bargained for as they follow thrill-seekers on a haunted hayride. Fear and death plague those who enter and those who seek the past. But can it all lead to a better place?
title: Hellbilly Hollow
